| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/templates` | List WhatsApp message templates. Filter: `?status=` (approved, pending, rejected). | Bearer | `whatsapp:templates:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/templates` | Create a new template (submits to Meta for approval) | Bearer | `whatsapp:templates:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/templates/{id}` | Get template detail (status, language, components) | Bearer | `whatsapp:templates:read` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/templates/{id}` | Update template (resubmits for approval) | Bearer | `whatsapp:templates:write` |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/templates/{id}` | Delete template | Bearer | `whatsapp:templates:delete` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/conversations` | List conversations. Filter: `?status=` (open, closed), `?contactId=`, `?assigneeId=`, `?search=`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:conversations:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/conversations/{id}` | Get conversation detail with messages. Include: `contact`, `messages`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:conversations:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/conversations/{id}/messages` | Send a message in a conversation. Body: `{ "type": "text", "content": "..." }` or `{ "type": "template", "template_id": "...", "params": {...} }`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:conversations:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/conversations/{id}/actions/close` | Close a conversation | Bearer | `whatsapp:conversations:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/conversations/{id}/actions/assign` | Assign conversation to a user. Body: `{ "assignee_id": "..." }`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:conversations:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/broadcasts` | List broadcast campaigns. Filter: `?status=`, `?createdAfter=`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:broadcasts:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/broadcasts` | Create a broadcast campaign. Body: `{ "template_id": "...", "segment_id": "...", "scheduled_at": "..." }`. | Bearer | `whatsapp:broadcasts:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/broadcasts/{id}` | Get broadcast detail (stats: sent, delivered, read, replied) | Bearer | `whatsapp:broadcasts:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/broadcasts/{id}/actions/send` | Dispatch broadcast (queue all messages via BullMQ) | Bearer | `whatsapp:broadcasts:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/whatsapp/broadcasts/{id}/actions/cancel` | Cancel scheduled broadcast | Bearer | `whatsapp:broadcasts:write` |

