### Trocas & Devolucoes (`/api/v1/trocas`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges` | List exchanges/returns. Filter: `?status=` (requested, approved, shipped_back, received, completed, rejected), `?type=` (exchange, return), `?orderId=`, `?contactId=`, `?createdAfter=`. | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges` | Create exchange/return request (admin-initiated) | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}` | Get exchange/return detail. Include: `order`, `contact`, `items`, `timeline`, `shipping_label`. | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:read` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}` | Update exchange (notes, items) | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}/actions/approve` | Approve exchange/return request | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}/actions/reject` | Reject exchange/return. Body: `{ "reason": "..." }`. | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}/actions/generate-return-label` | Generate return shipping label via Melhor Envio | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}/actions/mark-received` | Mark returned items as received in warehouse | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/exchanges/{id}/actions/complete` | Complete exchange (ship replacement) or return (issue refund/credit) | Bearer | `trocas:exchanges:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/trocas/store-credits` | List store credits. Filter: `?contactId=`, `?status=` (active, used, expired). | Bearer | `trocas:store-credits:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/trocas/store-credits` | Issue store credit manually. Body: `{ "contact_id": "...", "amount_cents": 5000, "reason": "..." }`. | Bearer | `trocas:store-credits:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/trocas/store-credits/{id}` | Get store credit detail (balance, transactions) | Bearer | `trocas:store-credits:read` |

#### Public (customer-facing exchange request)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/public/trocas/request` | Customer submits exchange/return request. Body: `{ "order_number": "...", "cpf": "...", "items": [...], "reason": "..." }`. | Public | — |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/public/trocas/status/{requestCode}` | Check exchange/return status by request code | Public | — |

