| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/clawdbot/prompts/{id}` | Update a prompt template | Bearer | `clawdbot:prompts:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/clawdbot/chat-log` | List recent chat interactions. Filter: `?channelId=`, `?userId=`, `?createdAfter=`. | Bearer | `clawdbot:chat-log:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/clawdbot/settings` | Get bot settings (default channel, response style, enabled modules) | Bearer | `clawdbot:settings:read` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/clawdbot/settings` | Update bot settings | Bearer | `clawdbot:settings:write` |

---

### Dashboard / Beacon (`/api/v1/dashboard`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/overview` | Get executive dashboard metrics. Query: `?period=7d` or `?startDate=&endDate=`. Returns: revenue, orders, AOV, conversion rate, top products. | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/sales` | Get sales metrics (revenue by day, payment method breakdown, channel breakdown). Query: `?period=`. | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/inventory` | Get inventory metrics (total value, low stock alerts, turnover). | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/crm` | Get CRM metrics (new contacts, RFM distribution, repurchase rate, churn rate). Query: `?period=`. | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/production` | Get production metrics (active OPs, on-time rate, stage bottlenecks). | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/metrics/financial` | Get financial metrics (DRE summary, margin, reconciliation status). Query: `?period=`. | Bearer | `dashboard:metrics:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions` | List War Room sessions. Filter: `?dropId=`, `?status=` (upcoming, live, ended). | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions` | Create a War Room session for a drop. Body: `{ "drop_id": "...", "starts_at": "..." }`. | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions/{id}` | Get War Room session detail (drop info, start time, live stats) | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions/{id}/actions/start` | Start War Room session (begins SSE broadcasting) | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:write` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions/{id}/actions/end` | End War Room session (stops SSE, generates summary) | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/war-room/sessions/{id}/summary` | Get post-War-Room summary (total revenue, units sold, peak sales/min) | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dashboard/panels` | List dashboard panels (user-configurable widgets) | Bearer | `dashboard:panels:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dashboard/panels` | Create a custom panel | Bearer | `dashboard:panels:write` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/dashboard/panels/{id}` | Update panel (position, size, data source, filters) | Bearer | `dashboard:panels:write` |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/dashboard/panels/{id}` | Delete custom panel | Bearer | `dashboard:panels:delete` |

---

### DAM (`/api/v1/dam`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dam/assets` | List assets. Filter: `?folderId=`, `?type=` (image, video, document), `?tag=`, `?search=`. Sort: `-createdAt`, `name`, `size`. | Bearer | `dam:assets:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dam/assets` | Upload a new asset (multipart form). Generates thumbnails on upload. | Bearer | `dam:assets:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dam/assets/{id}` | Get asset detail (URL, thumbnails, metadata, tags, usage). | Bearer | `dam:assets:read` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/dam/assets/{id}` | Update asset metadata (name, tags, folder, alt text) | Bearer | `dam:assets:write` |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/dam/assets/{id}` | Delete asset (removes from R2) | Bearer | `dam:assets:delete` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dam/assets/{id}/actions/move` | Move asset to a different folder. Body: `{ "folder_id": "..." }`. | Bearer | `dam:assets:write` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dam/assets/{id}/download` | Get signed download URL (time-limited) | Bearer | `dam:assets:read` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dam/folders` | List folders. Filter: `?parentId=` (null for root). | Bearer | `dam:folders:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dam/folders` | Create a new folder | Bearer | `dam:folders:write` |
| `PATCH` | `/api/v1/dam/folders/{id}` | Update folder (rename, move) | Bearer | `dam:folders:write` |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/dam/folders/{id}` | Delete folder (must be empty or cascade) | Bearer | `dam:folders:delete` |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/dam/tags` | List asset tags | Bearer | `dam:tags:read` |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/dam/tags` | Create a new tag | Bearer | `dam:tags:write` |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/dam/tags/{id}` | Delete tag | Bearer | `dam:tags:delete` |

---

### Internal Service-to-Service (`/internal/*`)

> **These endpoints are NOT exposed publicly.** They are internal API routes used for cross-module communication within the monorepo. All `/internal/*` routes are protected by a shared service key and are never called from the frontend.
>
> Internal endpoints are documented in each module's spec file (section 6). They follow the same envelope pattern but use API Key auth instead of Bearer tokens.

| Module | Key Internal Endpoints | Called By |
|--------|----------------------|-----------|
| CRM | `/internal/contacts/upsert-from-order`, `/internal/contacts/update-financials`, `/internal/automations/trigger` | Checkout, ERP |
| Creators | `/internal/creators/validate-coupon`, `/internal/creators/check-anti-fraud`, `/internal/creators/attribute-sale`, `/internal/creators/adjust-commission`, `/internal/creators/detect-post` | Checkout, Trocas, Instagram polling |
| ERP | `/internal/orders/create-from-checkout`, `/internal/inventory/production-entry`, `/internal/inventory/return-entry`, `/internal/nfe/emit-return`, `/internal/inventory/reserve`, `/internal/inventory/release`, `/internal/shipping/generate-label` | Checkout, PCP, Trocas, B2B |
| WhatsApp | `/internal/send-template`, `/internal/send-text` | CRM automations, Inbox |
| Inbox | `/internal/inbound/whatsapp`, `/internal/inbound/email` | WhatsApp Engine, Resend webhook |
| DAM | `/internal/assets/from-ugc`, `/internal/assets/by-collection/:id` | Marketing Intelligence, PCP |
| Trocas | `/internal/store-credits/validate`, `/internal/store-credits/redeem` | Checkout |
| Tarefas | `/internal/tasks/from-pcp`, `/internal/tasks/by-source/:id` | PCP |
| PCP | `/internal/stock-entry-complete` | ERP |

