|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/webhooks/mercado-pago` | Mercado Pago payment notifications | Signature | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/webhooks/melhor-envio` | Melhor Envio shipping status updates | Signature | — |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/webhooks/instagram` | Instagram subscription verification (challenge) | Public | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/webhooks/instagram` | Instagram subscription updates (mentions, comments) | Signature | — |

