### SSE Streams (`/api/v1/sse`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/sse/notifications` | User notification stream (Flare) | Bearer | Any authenticated |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/sse/war-room/{sessionId}` | Drop War Room live data stream | Bearer | `dashboard:war-room:read` |

