### Global Search (`/api/v1/search`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/search` | Global search across all modules. Query: `?q=` (tsvector full-text), `?modules=erp,crm` (optional scope). Returns grouped results by module. Rate limited: 30/min. | Bearer | Any authenticated (results filtered by user permissions) |

---

### Auth (`/api/v1/auth`)

| Method | Path | Description | Auth | Permission |
|--------|------|-------------|------|------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/login` | Login with email + password. Returns access token + sets refresh cookie. | Public | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/logout` | Logout. Clears refresh cookie, invalidates tokens. | Bearer | Any authenticated |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/refresh` | Refresh access token using refresh cookie. | Cookie | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/forgot-password` | Send password reset email. Body: `{ "email": "..." }`. | Public | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/reset-password` | Reset password with token. Body: `{ "token": "...", "password": "..." }`. | Public | — |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/auth/change-password` | Change own password. Body: `{ "current_password": "...", "new_password": "..." }`. | Bearer | Any authenticated |

---

*This document is the single source of truth for API design in LUMN. Every endpoint must conform to the patterns described here. When in doubt, reference this document before implementing.*
